# Roadmap

## Phase 0 — UI Prototype

Goal: Fully functional UI without real AI

Features:

- Chat interface
- Theme system structure
- Avatar rendering
- Fake responses (mock)

Contributors needed:

- Android UI developers
- Designers

---

## Phase 1 — Local AI Integration

Goal: Real local inference

Features:

- llama.cpp Android integration
- GGUF model loading
- Token streaming
- Basic settings

Contributors needed:

- NDK developers
- llama.cpp integration specialists

---

## Phase 2 — Voice Integration

Features:

- Speech-to-text
- Text-to-speech
- Voice selection per theme

---

## Phase 3 — Memory

Features:

- Local conversation memory
- Memory controls
- Export/delete memory

---

## Phase 4 — Theme Ecosystem

Features:

- Install/remove themes
- Theme validation
- Theme sharing

---

## Phase 5 — Optimization

Features:

- Performance improvements
- Battery optimizations
- Device-specific tuning
